node.text: Our first Instagram Live with our co-founder & CCO Anna Bond! She talks about our founding, answers questions, shared favorite products and give sneak peeks at upcoming goods.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Rifle Paper Co. on July 22, 2021 tagging @annariflebond, @riflepaperco, @target, and @gillettevenus. May be an image of cosmetics and flower.

node.text: We’ve heard that a few of you have already spotted these in the wild! We are excited to share that we are partnering with @GilletteVenus to bring a little beauty to the everyday with a collection of razors, blades, and shaving cream featuring our signature florals 🌸 The collection is available exclusively @Target and Target.com. Swipe to see the full lineup of products 🛁 #VenusxRiflePaperCo #riflepaperco
